# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PhaseCraft – Environment Variables
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Copy this file to `.env` for local development.
# For GitHub Pages deployment, add each variable as a repository secret:
#   https://docs.github.com/en/actions/security-guides/encrypted-secrets
#
# The GitHub Actions deploy workflow reads these secrets and exposes them to
# Vite as VITE_* variables so the browser can call AI providers directly
# (no backend server is required on GitHub Pages).
# ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

# Z.AI API key (used for the "z.ai" model / glm-5)
# Obtain from: https://z.ai
ZAI_API_KEY=your_zai_api_key_here

# Kimi API key (used for the "k2p5" model)
# Obtain from: https://platform.moonshot.cn
KIMI_API_KEY=your_kimi_api_key_here

# Anthropic API key (used for Claude Sonnet models)
# Obtain from: https://console.anthropic.com
# Note: Anthropic blocks direct browser requests unless you use an OAuth token
# (tokens starting with "sk-ant-oat" work from browsers via the OAuth beta).
ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=your_anthropic_api_key_here
